hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 流体动力学速率和密度-温度关系
   $$\lambda_{\rm hydro}=C_H\sqrt{G\,\rho},\qquad \rho=C_\rho\,T^3.$$  
   因此
   $$\lambda_{\rm hydro}
     =C_H\sqrt{G\,C_\rho\,T^3}
     =C_H\sqrt{G\,C_\rho}\;T^{3/2}.$$

2. 弱相互作用速率
   $$\lambda_{\rm weak}
     =C_W\,\frac{G_F^2}{\hbar}\Bigl(\frac{k_B T}{\hbar c}\Bigr)^5
     =C_W\,\frac{G_F^2\,k_B^5}{\hbar^6\,c^5}\;T^5.$$

3. 冻结条件 $\lambda_{\rm weak}=\lambda_{\rm hydro}$
   $$C_W\,\frac{G_F^2\,k_B^5}{\hbar^6\,c^5}\;T^5
     =C_H\sqrt{G\,C_\rho}\;T^{3/2}.$$

4. 求解 $T_f$
   $$T_f^{5-\tfrac32}
     =T_f^{\tfrac{7}{2}}
     =\frac{C_H\sqrt{G\,C_\rho}\;\hbar^6\,c^5}
           {C_W\,G_F^2\,k_B^5},$$  
   $$T_f
     =\biggl(\frac{C_H\sqrt{G\,C_\rho}\,\hbar^6\,c^5}
                   {C_W\,G_F^2\,k_B^5}\biggr)^{\tfrac{2}{7}}.$$
